      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used for FEA (Ansys Mechanical) is under documented version control with regression test suite; FDA-validated solver version employed throughout.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R2022 R2 used under ISO 9001-compliant QMS. Version-controlled input decks archived in validated PLM system. Regression tests cover linear static and contact-nonlinear solution paths relevant to this analysis."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
