      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver benchmarked against NAFEMS standard problems; patch test and cantilever beam solutions within 0.1% of analytic reference.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical passes NAFEMS LE1, LE3, and NL1 benchmark problems. Internal patch test confirms element formulation correctness. Results documented in solver verification report SVR-2022-001."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
