    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3 due to single-offset F1717 testing; this gap is accepted given established regulatory precedent and the conservative nature of the standard test configuration. Overall model credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
